26.000Z","msg":"每對顏色係線內係twisted pair <br />\nCat 5 同 cat 5e 嘅分别係每條線圈數同線材<br />\n可以改善crosstalk同 interference問題<br />\n大部份cat 5 同cat 5e 都差唔多, 只係條線一長就會出現明顯差别<br />\nCat5e 就係話係合規格情況下, 理論可以行到 giga<br />\nCat 5 行唔行到giga 就睇你運數, 但理論上100mb 係保證到<br />\n<br />\n而係廠方角度, 成本差唔多下, 已經好少搵到cat 5線"},{"pid":"097611afed95071a1eabdcd0b6bd7ba153432708","tid":1507614,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c0b704cc881bfe8f18bc8064c3335c018642f07","tid":1507614,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc7ec554aa6a2de3d627a13bbfeea9a15bda7d79","tid":1507614,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c399c48b92cbd095fba1ec70cb6957ce7db755e","tid":1507614,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"轉灣呢就真係好難講，你轉個九十度又係轉，打蛇餅又係轉，但以我理解唔係打蛇餅就無乜大影響<br />\n而長度，cat5e個標準係100米內有效，我當你條線真係偷工減料打個對折都50米，點可能30米就衰減九成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"亂鳩GOOGLE<br />\nCat5e Maximum Speed for Voice or Data Applications<br />\nCat 5e can support network operating speeds of 10 Mbps, 100 Mbps or 1000 Mbps. The gigabit rates are the maximum speed for Cat5e cable. When used for voice and data applications below max rate, Category 5e has a cable length limitation of 100 metres. If the cable is running at Cat5e max speed, this length limit drops to 50 metres.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.comms-express.com/infozone/article/cat5e-max-speed-cat5e-cable-speed/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.comms-express.com%2Finfozone%2Farticle%2Fcat5e-max-speed-cat5e-cable-speed%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=31ef3121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.comms-express.com/infozone/arti